{"tid":2176322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴威今日登陸大陸遼寧省，東北100年以來最強颱風！","createTime":"2020-08-27T04:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T04:50:22.000Z","uid":66087,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a516362139c59be784cdbe757df47fb2257639a","tid":2176322,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZXw7dxT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZXw7dxT.jpg&h=e0934fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年太平洋第 8 號颱風「巴威」於今（ 27 日）上午 8 點 30 分左右，登陸遼寧省，登陸時中心附近最大風力達到 12 級，同時也是自 1949 年以來，首個將真正直接侵襲中國東北的颱風。丹東、大連等鄰近地區的海上航運已全數暫停。<br />\n<br />\n陸媒報導，巴威颱風將以每小時 50 公里左右的速度向北偏東方向移動，登陸時強度為颱風級，預計 27 日午後到夜間將穿越中國東北 3 省。"},{"pid":"1f4a7218cbbc2f52f6e2278f3179645f3fbc011d","tid":2176322,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:31:59.000Z","msg":"東北今次玩完了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddf36f49b77993647c83618668b858a1f57f1a4","tid":2176322,"uid":17799,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:35:59.000Z","msg":"今次真係你鹿死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814721de87121c786987a54c03e7e4980fa360fa","tid":2176322,"uid":265943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"豆腐渣工程即刻出現"},{"pid":"f46dfc4fb5a10b9cd95281d280b2bbb8e7ea2a3c","tid":2176322,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"春春叫到, 個天咪響應下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ea8a2fb798b0a16f99310fc29ab7fbf23fc4de","tid":2176322,"uid":314790,"like":0,"